Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:43.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:48.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:57.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:23:01.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:11.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:20.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:29.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:39.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:46.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:47.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:53.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般闪耀于汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:43.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:48.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:57.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:23:01.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:11.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:20.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:29.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:39.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:46.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:47.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:53.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:01.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}月亮在轻轻低语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:06.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}以谁也听不到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur3}不断满涨的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:14.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}消失渐远的记忆中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:20.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}星星在密密记述着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}以谁也无法解读的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:29.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}无限的语言的涡旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:34.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}千亿本书由此诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:41.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}我的天空无限广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}时间在飞速的镌刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}毫无所知的虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:56.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}汇聚的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:59.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:06.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:11.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}扬起晦涩难懂的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:17.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}至少将这声音传至天际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:22.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}太阳也终会升起吧
